OL,3,CWhy are you still paying for a
OL,4,Clandline you do not need?
OL,6,F"More importantly, what consumers look
OL,7,Ffor is transparency, if there is
OL,8,Ftransparency in the pricing, then
OL,9,Fpeople can make a judgement call as to
OL,10,Fwhether they agree to it or not."
OL,12,FJersey Telecom (JT) owns the island's
OL,13,Fbroadband infrastructure used by all
OL,14,Flocal operators.
